    "description": "《破月勇者》是一款回合制策略和小规模战斗战术游戏，由《深海迷航》系列的制作团队 Unknown Worlds 开发。游戏背景设置在畅销科幻小说家布兰登·山德森打造的广阔科幻世界中，旨在提供真正的数字化微缩模型体验。通过易上手的回合制竞技玩法、充满沉浸感的美术设计、引人入胜的背景故事和深度自定义功能，《破月勇者》将为所有类型的玩家提供丰富多样的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/2fb357b26c3704dc071380252730772e.poster.avif?t=1726810180\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/2fb357b26c3704dc071380252730772e.webm?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/2fb357b26c3704dc071380252730772e.mp4?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>回合制桌面战术玩法：</strong>指挥你的单位，展开快节奏的回合制小规模策略战斗。与其他玩家或 AI 进行对战，或是游玩单人 roguelike 冒险模式“头目挑战”。简单有趣，易上手，难放手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/59af061e5762c0fed3755672b8e9e914.poster.avif?t=1726810180\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/59af061e5762c0fed3755672b8e9e914.webm?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/59af061e5762c0fed3755672b8e9e914.mp4?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>打造你的阵容：</strong>没有两个单位是完全一样的，也没有两套阵容的玩法是完全一样的。每一种单位都拥有独特的技能组合、游戏风格、角色性格等特点。使用丰富多样的单位打造不同特性的阵容，享受新奇的游戏体验，创造终极战队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/95e9a19be8822d65d801774560dd8f20.poster.avif?t=1726810180\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/95e9a19be8822d65d801774560dd8f20.webm?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/95e9a19be8822d65d801774560dd8f20.mp4?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>涂装你的队员：</strong>你可以通过单位涂装功能发挥你的创造力，体验原汁原味的微缩模型涂装过程，同时又不会受到真实世界的约束。游戏提供的专业数字涂装工具已经远超传统方式所能做到的事（撤销！遮罩！缩放！），能够为玩家营造表达自我的完美空间。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/30ec5bee56dc5306e31a3a95f727222c.poster.avif?t=1726810180\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/30ec5bee56dc5306e31a3a95f727222c.webm?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/845890/extras/30ec5bee56dc5306e31a3a95f727222c.mp4?t=1726810180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索远界宇宙：</strong>远界宇宙是一个由受人喜爱的科幻作家布兰登·山德森所打造的虚构世界，拥有丰富而多样的角色和文化。你还可以通过由获奖作家丹·威尔斯所创作的广播剧，由知名配音演员配音的游戏内对话旁白，以及包含各种背景故事的可解锁典籍来探索《破月勇者》的庞大世界。",
